      "content": "but that's just a way to cope, isn't it? a way to distract ourselves from the math. if we look at it objectively, if existence has a net value of zero because there is no purpose, then choosing to stop existing is just a neutral decision. it's like choosing between zero and zero. it's actually more logical to just opt out than to keep struggling for something that isn't even there. don't you think?",
